# Commit Attribution

When working in this repository, do not add AI, Cursor, Codex, Claude, or tool
co-author trailers to commits.

Never add this trailer:

```text
Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
```

Use the configured human Git identity for commits unless the user explicitly
asks for a different attribution policy.
